like this again.

37:54.773 --> 37:56.107
You understand?

37:56.107 --> 37:59.152
♪♪

37:59.152 --> 38:01.488
You don't know me.

38:01.488 --> 38:07.619
♪♪

38:07.619 --> 38:09.496
