38:40.568 --> 38:42.278
Mm‐hmm.

38:42.278 --> 38:44.447
Yeah.

38:44.447 --> 38:46.032
Be in my room.

38:47.492 --> 38:52.080
♪♪

38:52.080 --> 38:54.624
Babe, I'm sorry our fun day
kind of sucked,

38:54.624 --> 38:58.127
