39:01.047 --> 39:02.298
Let me see.

39:02.298 --> 39:03.591
[ Laughs ]

39:03.591 --> 39:04.843
[ Laughs ]

39:04.843 --> 39:06.636
Oh, man.

39:06.636 --> 39:08.137
Thank you.

39:08.137 --> 39:10.682
For making me laugh
today.

39:13.017 --> 39:15.728
I think I understand the reason
people like Crocodilze.

39:15.728 --> 39:20.817
It's comfortable and familiar
and it's always there.

39:20.817 --> 39:22.318
Kind of like you and me.

39:22.318 --> 39:23.736
Mm.

39:23.736 --> 39:25.530
You saying
I'm like your chicken Parm?

39:25.530 --> 39:27.740
Mmm, yep.

39:27.740 --> 39:29.033
Just as delicious, too.

39:29.033 --> 39:30.118
Oh.

39:32.161 --> 39:33.538
